            <thetext>If the current page is still loading Webkit under MacOS does not replace the current page with the new one.
Correct this wrong behaviour by manually stop the loading of the current page for Webkit/MacOS.

Thanks to Tino for the bugfix!</thetext>
          </long_desc>
