            <thetext>Fixed in both legacy_0_7_x (qx.ui.embed.Iframe) and trunk (qx.bom.Iframe) by adding a call of &quot;stop&quot; when the page should be replaced in Webkit/MacOS.
Other browsers and platforms are not affected AFAIK.

Revision #18434</thetext>
